; Test commodity comparison with mixed annotated/unannotated lots
; Covers commodity.cc lines 389-396 (annotation presence asymmetry)

2024/01/15 Buy annotated lot
    Assets:Stocks    10 AAPL {$150}
    Assets:Cash

2024/02/20 Buy unannotated lot
    Assets:Stocks    5 AAPL
    Assets:Cash

test bal --lots --no-total Assets:Stocks
              5 AAPL
      10 AAPL {$150}  Assets:Stocks
end test
